text: Dorota Pykosz (born 22 October 1978) is a Polish volleyball player. She played at the 2009 Women's European Volleyball Championship and 2009 FIVB World Grand Prix. She played for Polski Cukier Muszynianka Muszyna, TPS Rumia, Trefl Sopot, and Stal Mielec. == References == Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Polish volleyball players
